uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.motor

Interface IReasoner

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IClassifier, IReasonerDefault, NClassifier, ORClassifier

    public interface IReasoner
    Provides mechanisms for initialising the sets of slots for specific instance-level frames, and for dynamically updating those sets based on the current states of the frames.

    Updates to the slot-sets can be of the following types:

    • Addition of new slots
    • Removal of existing slots
    • Updates to slot value-types
    • Updates to slot activations
    • Updates to slot editabilities
